@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

@section PageCss {
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/website.css" />
}

<section class="aboutus-header">
    <h1>About Quality Copiers & Printers</h1>
    <p>Your reliable partner in office automation solutions since 2007.</p>
</section>


<section class="aboutus-profile">
    <img src="~/images/AboutUs.png" alt="About us page image to change" />

    <div class="text-content">
    <h2>Company Profile</h2>
    <p>Quality Copiers was established more than fifteen years ago and has
        been under new ownership since October 2007. Our CEO has more than 
        thirty years of experience in the office automation industry and has worked for
        two of the industry giants until an opportunity afforded him to purchase this company.</p>

    <h2>Mission Statement</h2>
    <p>Our goal is to supply reliable, honest and cost effective service to 
        all our clients. Quality Copiers provides technical support, machine 
        sales and consumable sales for office automation equipment. Our clients 
        range from small to corporate companies, which also include copier dealers.</p>

    <h2>Our Expertise</h2>
    <p>Our specialty is Ricoh/Gestetner printers and copiers, but we have
        experience in servicing and maintaining various other brands like 
        HP-Hewlett Packard, Xerox, Minolta, Epson, Canon and many others.</p>
      
     <div class="buttons">
    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Contact" class="text-button">Contact Us</a>
    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Services" class="text-button">Our Services</a>
    </div>
    </div>
</section>

